# Incorrect error message displayed when email field is empty on Facebook login page

## Environment
Chrome 146.0.7680.80 (64-bit), Windows Desktop

## Steps to Reproduce

Open Facebook login page

Leave the email field empty

Enter any password into the password field

Click the Log In button

## Expected Result
System should display a validation message asking the user to enter an email or mobile number.

## Actual Result
System displays the message: “The email or mobile number you entered isn’t connected to an account.”

## Type
UX / Validation Issue
